        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "1. Al-Husayn from Muhammad has narrated from Mu‘alla’ ibn Muhammad from al-Hassan ibn Afi af-Washsha’ from Jamif ibn Darraj and Muhammad ibn Humran who has narrated the foiiowing: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘The free and slaves do not inherit each other.’” "
        ]
